                  <item xml:id="a5"><desc type="OwnershipNote"><locus target="#56r"/> and passim: name of secondary owner, Wäldä Giyorgis (written over the top of the original name which is erased). The names Akazǝyas and Wäldä Täklä Haymanot are inserted secondarily</desc></item>
